from: Ronaldo Vieira

I needed a data structure to represent a semantic model and so I came across 
Minsky's frames in the book Knowledge representation and reasoning by 
Ronald J. Brachman and Hector J. Levesque (chapter 8). 
Hope you can find it useful.

